news.article_text:
Wall Street analysts forecast that Verizon Communications (VZ) will report quarterly earnings of $1.19 per share in its upcoming release, pointing to no change from the year-ago quarter. It is anticipated that revenues will amount to $34.18 billion, exhibiting an increase of 2.5% compared to the year-ago quarter.

news.headline: T-Mobile Stock Falls Amid Worries Wireless Competition Will Intensify
news.summary: T-Mobile US (TMUS) on Thursday reported third-quarter earnings and revenue that edged by consensus estimates. The wireless services provider added more high-spending phone subscribers than expected. T-Mobile stock fell on the news and closed at 219.99.
news.article_text:
T-Mobile US (TMUS) on Thursday reported third-quarter earnings and revenue that edged by consensus estimates. The wireless services provider added more high-spending phone subscribers than expected. T-Mobile stock fell on the news.

Controlled by Deutsche Telekom (DTEGY), T-Mobile released Q3 earnings before the market open.
